This directory is a mirror of https://github.com/k1p1l0/claude-telegram-supercharged
(Apache-2.0), republished in this marketplace for easier installation.

Contents are synced from upstream `master` daily by
`.github/workflows/sync-telegram-supercharged.yml`. The only file owned by this
marketplace is `.claude-plugin/plugin.json`, which is regenerated on each sync.

Issues, feature requests, and contributions belong upstream, not here.
